## NPM Packages
- `@coveo/headless` — state management, engine, controllers (pinned to `^3.50.1`)
- No separate React wrapper (`@coveo/headless-react`) needed for client-side rendering; use vanilla `@coveo/headless` with the `useCoveoController` hook in `web/src/hooks/`
- Optional dev dependency: `playwright` + `tsx` in the **separate** `tools/seed-ml/` package — NOT installed by `web/`
